/** Usage

> git init .
> git remote add -f origin https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus-quickstarts.git
> git checkout e1e97bb3fdc333b85ddf53fa354b0d9e2915053b

> ./mill init

> rm kafka-avro-schema-quickstart/package.mill.yaml grpc-plain-text-quickstart/package.mill.yaml grpc-tls-quickstart/package.mill.yaml # skip subprojects with quarkus codegen. Not yet implemented in mill.

> ./mill __.compile # Just compile all modules. `quarkusRunJar` task fails for some

*/
